[2026-03-13T14:43:44Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012ovGAixGPeBPzTwr5fAY3p","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package dsl\n     2→\n     3→type TokenType int\n     4→\n     5→const (\n     6→\tTokenEOF     TokenType = iota\n     7→\tTokenIllegal\n     8→\tTokenIdent\n     9→\tTokenInt\n    10→\tTokenString\n    11→\tTokenLBrace\n    12→\tTokenRBrace\n    13→\tTokenLBracket\n    14→\tTokenRBracket\n    15→\tTokenLParen\n    16→\tTokenRParen\n    17→\tTokenComma\n    18→\tTokenEquals\n    19→\tTokenArrow\n    20→\tTokenColon\n    21→\tTokenDot\n    22→)\n    23→\n    24→func (t TokenType) String() string {\n    25→\tswitch t {\n    26→\tcase TokenEOF:\n    27→\t\treturn \"EOF\"\n    28→\tcase TokenIllegal:\n    29→\t\treturn \"ILLEGAL\"\n    30→\tcase TokenIdent:\n    31→\t\treturn \"IDENT\"\n    32→\tcase TokenInt:\n    33→\t\treturn \"INT\"\n    34→\tcase TokenString:\n    35→\t\treturn \"STRING\"\n    36→\tcase TokenLBrace:\n    37→\t\treturn \"LBRACE\"\n    38→\tcase TokenRBrace:\n    39→\t\treturn \"RBRACE\"\n    40→\tcase TokenLBracket:\n    41→\t\treturn \"LBRACKET\"\n    42→\tcase TokenRBracket:\n    43→\t\treturn \"RBRACKET\"\n    44→\tcase TokenLParen:\n    45→\t\treturn \"LPAREN\"\n    46→\tcase TokenRParen:\n    47→\t\treturn \"RPAREN\"\n    48→\tcase TokenComma:\n    49→\t\treturn \"COMMA\"\n    50→\tcase TokenEquals:\n    51→\t\treturn \"EQUALS\"\n    52→\tcase TokenArrow:\n    53→\t\treturn \"ARROW\"\n    54→\tcase TokenColon:\n    55→\t\treturn \"COLON\"\n    56→\tcase TokenDot:\n    57→\t\treturn \"DOT\"\n    58→\tdefault:\n    59→\t\treturn \"UNKNOWN\"\n    60→\t}\n    61→}\n    62→\n    63→type Token struct {\n    64→\tType    TokenType\n    65→\tLiteral string\n    66→\tLine    int\n    67→\tCol     int\n    68→}\n    69→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PB2FoeV4tsuHgPF56K4Qdh","session_id":"87510e8f-028e-4687-9903-d33073502bb8","uuid":"56ff9ba3-f43c-4dff-95fc-e09783f7c652"}
