[2026-03-13T14:43:44Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0119GCouprWDxM75vCYuNV2H","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspace/docs/workflows.md:**Container workflows** (`.cloche/*.cloche` except `host.cloche`) — Run inside a Docker\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:**Host workflows** (`.cloche/host.cloche`) — Run on the host machine as the daemon\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:A single `host.cloche` file may contain **multiple named workflows**. The daemon\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:until it completes. Only available in host workflows (`host.cloche`).\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    prompt = file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    prompt = file(\".cloche/prompts/fix.md\")\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:**`host {}`** — For host workflows (`host.cloche`). Sets agent defaults for agent steps\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:A three-phase `host.cloche` with separate `list-tasks`, `main`, and `finalize`\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:# .cloche/host.cloche — runs on the host machine\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    run     = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    run     = \"bash .cloche/scripts/prepare-prompt.sh\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:    run     = \"bash .cloche/scripts/push-for-review.sh\"\n/workspace/docs/workflows.md:`host.cloche` file may contain multiple named workflows; the daemon orchestrates them\n/workspace/docs/INSTALL.md:# Run a quick test from any git repository with a .cloche/ directory\n/workspace/docs/INSTALL.md:- [Workflow DSL reference](workflows.md) — full syntax for `.cloche` files\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:workflow graph in the `.cloche` DSL, Cloche copies your project into a Docker\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:Workflow files use the `.cloche` extension and live in `.cloche/`. The first step\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:    prompt = file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:| `feedback` | string | Set to `\"true\"` to include `.cloche/output/*.log` content in the prompt. |\n/workspace/docs/USAGE.md:prompt = file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PB2FoeV4tsuHgPF56K4Qdh","session_id":"87510e8f-028e-4687-9903-d33073502bb8","uuid":"defa8bd4-b74c-4d0e-a3b6-8a2818021e9f"}
